Name: Average resolution time difference between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Accepted + In Progress'", 'end': "activity == 'Accepted + Wait - User'", 'aggregation': 'median'}

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed' without entering 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all variants leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E8EF99C100> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' leading directly to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' followed by 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before resolution
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Average lead time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Closed' across high impact cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Median time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to the first occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Accepted + In Progress'", 'end': "activity == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'", 'aggregation': 'median'}

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for cases resolved within the same day
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' between cases with 'Low' and 'High' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'Low' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Total cumulative time of 'Accepted + In Progress' for all cases in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Distribution of 'Accepted + In Progress' duration across different variants leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average delay time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait' in cases exceeding expected resolution time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Longest and shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases in the event log
Time efficiency of 'Accepted + In Progress' leading to 'Completed + Resolved' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress' leading to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average handling time of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to any 'Completed' status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
